<s> We developed a C binding using the Java bindings as a guide.  </s>
<s> The first argument is always the object (which is a vtable like self descriptive object), and overloaded method names were extended to include type in the name: value = PDOMgetValue(textObject); PDOMsetValue(textObject, "new value"); etc...  </s>
<s> It would seem a C++ binding based on the Java bindings as starting place would be straight forward.  </s>
